column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid, p.ra, p.dec,  p.deVMag_u, p.deVMagErr_u, p.deVMag_z, p.deVMagErr_z, g.lgm_tot_p5#,  p.z, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,  s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift,  s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN galSpecExtra AS g ON g.specobjid = p.specobjid WHERE   s.z BETWEEN # AND #  AND g.lgm_tot_p5# > #
